Solid–liquid iron partitioning in Earth’s deep mantle
<g id="1">Denis Andrault</g>,
<g id="1">Sylvain Petitgirard</g>,
<g id="1">Giacomo Lo Nigro</g>,
<g id="1">Jean-Luc Devidal</g>,
<g id="1">Giulia Veronesi</g>,
<g id="1">Gaston Garbarino</g> &
<g id="1">Mohamed Mezouar</g>
<g id="1">Nature</g> <g id="2">volume</g><g id="3"> 487</g>, <g id="4">pages</g>354–357 (2012)<g id="5">Cite this article</g>
3240 <g id="1">Accesses</g>
